Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Why it Costs so Much to Rebuild Iraq
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00spzqr
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 Sep 2003
Alistair Cooke asks why it is costing so much to rebuild Iraq and seizes the launch of a four-bladed razor to analyse the process of shaving.